#make no-member-named errors bright red
s|\(.*\):\([0-9]\+\): error: 'class \([^']*\)' has no member named '\([^']*\)'|\o033[1;31m\n>> Error at \1 - line \2\n    \o033[0mClass\n        \o033[1;34m\3\o033[0m\n    has no member named\n        \o033[1;34m\4\o033[0m|g
s|\(.*\):\([0-9]\+\): error: 'struct \([^']*\)' has no member named '\([^']*\)'|\o033[1;31m\n>> Error at \1 - line \2\n    \o033[0mStruct\n        \o033[1;34m\3\o033[0m\n    has no member named\n        \o033[1;34m\4\o033[0m|g

#make not of class type errors bright red
s|\(.*\):\([0-9]\+\): error: '\([^']*\)' does not have class type|\o033[1;31m\n>> Error at \1 - line \2\n    \o033[1;34m\3\o033[0m\n        does not have class type\n            \o033[1;32mHint : have you forgotten function braces?\o033[0m|g


#format candidates
