s|\(.*\):\([0-9]\+\): error: candidate[^:]*: \(.*\)|    Candidates are\n        \o033[1;32m\3\o033[0m\n            from \1 - line \2|g
s|\(.*\):\([0-9]\+\): error:  \+\(.*\)|        \o033[1;32m\3\o033[0m\n            from \1 - line \2|g
s|\(.*\):\([0-9]\+\): note: candidates are[^:]*: \(.*\)|    Candidates are\n        \o033[1;32m\3\o033[0m\n            from \1 - line \2|g
s|\(.*\):\([0-9]\+\): note:[ ]*\(.*\)|        \o033[1;32m\3\o033[0m\n            from \1 - line \2|g

